      • getSortOrder

        public SortOrder getSortOrder()
        Description copied from interface: FieldSort
        Return whether it is sorted in a natural "ascending" order or a natural "descending" order. For Strings, this is a locale-specific sort order. For numeric fields, it is lower numbers to higher numbers. For temporaral values, older values sort first in the ascending order.
        Specified by:
        getSortOrder in interface FieldSort
